####what i did before be able launching run_eval.sh

#install conda
wget https://repo.continuum.io/miniconda/Miniconda3-latest-Linux-x86_64.sh
bash Miniconda3-latest-Linux-x86_64.sh (+ follow instructions)



#create right env
conda create --name zerospeech python=2

#intstall zerospeech eval tools
pushd /home/getalp/besacier/BACKUP-JSALT/TOOLS
source activate zerospeech
pip install git+https://github.com/bootphon/tde@zerospeech2017 --user




Before launching run_eval.sh, you must do source activate zerospeech
(+ a few pip install MODULE to run)


